🔐 Security Best Practices
Encrypt EBS volumes for sensitive workloads
Delete unused volumes to avoid unnecessary costs
Ensure correct attachment permissions via IAM roles
Use snapshots for backup and recovery strategies
Restrict volume access within the correct VPC and AZ boundaries
💰 Cost Awareness

You are billed for:

Provisioned storage (GB per month)
Provisioned IOPS (for performance types)
Snapshots stored in S3

Always delete unused volumes and snapshots to avoid unnecessary charges.

